This is how to parse_music of music_string:
  Remember that notes is []
  Remember that current_count is 0
  Remember that i is 0
  Do this music_string's length times:
    When item i in music_string is "o", then:
      Increase current_count by 1
    But, if not:
      When current_count is more than 0, then:
        Add notes to current_count
        Remember that current_count is 0
      End when
    End when
    Increase i by 1
  End do
  When current_count is more than 0, then:
